{"tid":1177930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「官方公審」大陸將衝紅燈嘅人個樣放上大屏公審","createTime":"2019-05-30T05:30:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T05:58:30.000Z","uid":213252,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"42c0ed174e1eac13acbe37e3ebd2a9b4b0f696fa","tid":1177930,"uid":213252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T05:30:22.000Z","msg":"【太原人臉識別抓闖紅燈 未成年人照片未打碼上大屏 交警：一視同仁】5月25日，山西太原一路口設置了屏幕，曝光闖紅燈的行人。除了成年人的照片，還有未打馬賽克的未成年人照片展示在屏幕上。太原交警部門表示，未成年人和成年人是一樣的，只要違法闖紅燈就會被曝光展示一周左右，上大屏是一種警告的方式。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利害了我的國！！"},{"pid":"9199616c4bc295b27dc57a4a8e7652483886896b","tid":1177930,"uid":53687,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T05:31:05.000Z","msg":"德政，最好審埋隨地吐痰嘅人"},{"pid":"08b618f9a70b50c643e73e96aa4023f3e2529f66","tid":1177930,"uid":24730,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T05:31:53.000Z","msg":"中國人是要管的"},{"pid":"b6ed19d6a5a35c1d0d6f5f5e91d8a669e0b78877","tid":1177930,"uid":210729,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T05:31:54.000Z","msg":"香港都要咁啦 捉晒啲火車頭擺上網公審<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a8cf3b60b98dec66b834afc02d5ea2c643398b8","tid":1177930,"uid":29689,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T05:35:23.000Z","msg":"foresee 到大陸人會當宣傳易咁用<br />\n舉埋牌show 埋商品有大銀幕幫你賣足一個禮拜廣告<br />\n希望唔好有人亂舉平板六四牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1ff1e3cc3ba9489ebce037f37d6c3e46c7ea1db","tid":1177930,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T05:58:30.000Z","msg":"支那高科技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支那狗唔管下周圍屙屎架"}]}